dct_title_s: A view of the division of the land of Canaan and the situation of the city and sanctuary
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows drainage, territorial boundaries of the twelve tribes of Israel, places of historical interest.
Inset map: A map of Europe, Asia, and Africa to shew the central situation of the city of Jerusalem.
